clamav|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
clamav: clamav (Open Source antivirus scanner)
clamav:
clamav: Clam AntiVirus is a GPL antivirus toolkit for UNIX. The main purpose
clamav: is the integration with mailservers (attachment scanning). The package
clamav: provides a flexible and scalable multi-threaded daemon, a command line
clamav: scanner, and a tool for automatic updating via Internet.
clamav: This package includes the Sendmail interface to scan e-mail:
clamav: clamav-milter. Once installed, it's ready to go and can be started
clamav: with no modification. 
clamav: http://www.clamav.net/
